    MULTIPLICITY  3
    &MGRID
      CUTOFF 800
      NGRIDS 3
    &END MGRID
    &QS
      EPS_DEFAULT 1.0E-12
    &END QS
    &SCF
      EPS_SCF 1.0E-7
      MAX_SCF 2000
